metadata.name: Serenity
metadata.description:
Feelings are like waves, when you notice each one, there is tension in your mind and heart. Accepting everything that's going on, you're just swaying on the waves enjoying your time in the world. And a free consciousness gives peace and tranquility..

Original painting.
Oil on canvas.
20 x 20 cm

Year: 2021
NFT: 2580 x 2550 pixels

Solovyova Anastasia
